<font color="yellow">Ini bukan hariku.</font>

721
00:58:18,578 --> 00:58:20,808
<font color="yellow">Menyebalkan sekali.</font>

722
00:58:26,148 --> 00:58:27,748
<font color="yellow">Hei. Na Ri.</font>

723
00:58:30,148 --> 00:58:31,448
<font color="yellow">Itu Na Ri.</font>

724
00:58:32,178 --> 00:58:33,178
<font color="yellow">Masuklah.</font>

725
00:58:33,978 --> 00:58:34,978
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

726
00:59:04,778 --> 00:59:06,278
<font color="yellow">(Sweet Stranger dan Me)</font>

727
00:59:06,678 --> 00:59:08,308
<font color="yellow">Aku harap aku tidak melakukan kesalahan.</font>

728
00:59:08,478 --> 00:59:10,508
<font color="yellow">Siapa yang mengurungku dan kenapa?</font>

729
00:59:10,578 --> 00:59:12,678
<font color="yellow">Hei! Gil!</font>

730
00:59:12,848 --> 00:59:13,878
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

731
00:59:13,878 --> 00:59:17,278
<font color="yellow">Mereka mengirimi Na Ri dokumen itu.</font>

732
00:59:17,278 --> 00:59:18,708
<font color="yellow">Itu adalah Nan Gil.</font>

733
00:59:18,708 --> 00:59:21,648
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak akan datang dan melihatku
kecuali aku menyeretnya masuk.</font>

734
00:59:21,648 --> 00:59:24,248
<font color="yellow">Na Ri tidak ingat sama sekali, bukan?</font>

735
00:59:24,248 --> 00:59:25,508
<font color="yellow">Jual tanahnya sekarang.</font>

736
00:59:25,508 --> 00:59:28,378
<font color="yellow">Kau seharusnya mengambil uang itu dan lari.</font>

737
00:59:28,378 --> 00:59:30,048
<font color="yellow">Apa Na Ri tahu?</font>

738
00:59:30,048 --> 00:59:32,208
<font color="yellow">Ayah tiri? Kenapa orang psiko itu...</font>

739
00:59:32,208 --> 00:59:33,778
<font color="yellow">- Tentu saja.
- Apa yang dia katakan?</font>

740
00:59:34,078 --> 00:59:35,178
<font color="yellow">Dia bukan seorang penipu.</font>

741
00:59:35,578 --> 00:59:36,978
<font color="yellow">Aku rasa aku tahu siapa dia.</font>

